overview:
Rence Winetrout has nearly 20 years of experience leading mutli-channel e-Commerce, e-Marketing, and e-Business initiatives for premium, global consumer brands selling luxury goods, apparel, footwear, accessories, sporting goods, consumer electronics, and digital goods.

Rence has held leadership roles at a number of fortune 500 companies, including Apple Inc., adidas Group, TaylorMade Golf, adidas Golf, Checkpoint Software, and Borland International.
